com.github.kskelm.baringo.util

Interface RetrofittedImgur


  • public interface RetrofittedImgur
    This class is not meant to be seen by human eyes. It's the Retrofit2-compatible annotated interface calls used to connect with Imgur's API 3.
    Author:
    Kevin Kelm (triggur@gmail.com)
